latestIgtvVideos.title: HAPPY BIRTHDAY 🎈 BABY 😘
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Wishing you many more years of good health and prosperity❤️❤️ Thank you for living your life in a way that makes every day worth celebrating. Happiest of birthdays!💗💗💥 Having you in my life is really wonderful, you are not just a friend, you are like family  and I am sorry if I haven’t really been there for you when I should. Friendship isn’t always about partying, grooving and wasting some precious time. But also to give advice and listen to thoughts and opinions, all these you have done and still do. Truly you have been a great Sister for me💚 I love you unconditionally❣️❣️❣️. Because of you, I can say that I'm a better person who is made happier with you as my best friend. I hope that one day we'll be wreaking havoc and laughing in an old age home together, tripping each other over with our zimmer frames and walkers.💫💕💕💌💌💌 I LOVE YOU ❤️ Baby 🎈🎂
My doremon 💋🐱 my support system ❤️❤️❤️ my happy place ☺️ 💝 and once again ❤️ happiest birthday to you ❤️ Baby 🎂@its._.aafii._ ❤️❤️
